                                .Coffee & Tea .Bakeries .Breakfast & Brunch<br />
                                4181 Hamilton Ave Cincinnati, OH 45223
                            </p>
                            <p class="restaurant-rating">Rating: 4.5/5</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
